<p>I am trying to redirect to another page in the same domain from within iframe, the new page always loads inside the iframe. </p>  <p>This is the code in my iframe</p>  <pre><code>   window.top.location.href = '@(Url.Action("Result", "Payment", new { from = "timeout"}))'; </code></pre>  <p>I also tried </p>  <pre><code>window.parent.location.href= '@(Url.Action("Result", "Payment", new { from = "timeout"}))'; parent.location.href='@(Url.Action("Result", "Payment", new { from = "timeout"}))'; document.location.href='@(Url.Action("Result", "Payment", new { from = "timeout"}))'; window.parent.location.assign('@(Url.Action("Result", "Payment", new { from = "timeout"}))'); </code></pre>  <p>Is there any cross browser solution to this. My trials were on chrome</p>